channel.title: Problems wiith loading mopar
channel.description:
I have a problem loading mopar scape. I go to moparscape,org and then click yes\always for the java. then i wait wait wait and nothing comes up. nothing loads...
So i went and downloaded the client.. And when i go to run it i get ( Could not find the main class. Program will exit!) and the name of the error is Java Virtual Machine launcher..
What do i do. Im ok with figuring thing out on a computer... But this problem gets to me..
My friend tells me how fun it is and i'm bumbed out becouse i can't play it =(
Thanks.
